id: pm-zwpp
title: "Promote annotation and link primitives to the public SDK: comments, notes, learnings, files, docs, deps, append metadata"
description: "Typed SDK functions for item annotation/link facets — comment CRUD, notes/learnings append+list, file/doc link management, dependency edges, and append/body metadata. Linked-test execution is out of scope here and belongs to pm-oslr. Duplicate check: no existing annotation-primitive SDK item."
